2026-05-15T01:59:41.2795368Z 12    <!--
2026-05-15T01:59:41.2795749Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T01:59:41.2796099Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
